{"tid":2187993,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合國專家指港區國安法似乎損害法官及律師的獨立性","createTime":"2020-09-04T03:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T05:39:45.000Z","uid":241764,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a33803ad4d0ddf083f46c5f7102850fb8540e344","tid":2187993,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T03:37:16.000Z","msg":"聯合國7名人權專家去信中國政府，認為「港區國安法」侵犯了某些基本權利，擔心當局利用有關法例起訴香港的政治人物。<br />\n<br />\n聯署信認為，「港區國安法」的措施不符合中國根據國際法所承擔的法律義務，又對法例在關鍵部份欠缺精準，侵犯某些基本權利表達關注，擔心很多原本合法的捍衛人權活動，將會被視為非法，認為法例不應該用來限制受保護的基本自由，包括表達意見、言論自由及和平集會的權利，<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547798-20200904.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547798-20200904.htm&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=2bd3ee4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547798-20200904.htm&h=c302fd91\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547798-20200904.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b34fdff0527441616a25e5fce138252ef05295ca","tid":2187993,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T03:38:05.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實用 post ,樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想保護自己同埋身邊嘅人？即刻入嚟睇吓!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2185179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2185179</a